title: GOP lawmakers call for heavier sanctions against China’s Huawei, SMIC
description: Michael McCaul (R-Tex.) and other lawmakers suggested severe measures to tighten sanctions against China’s chip industry for allegedly violating U.S. export controls.

title: Supreme Court asked to pause limits on White House social media requests
description: The filing brings a long-simmering legal battle over the future of online speech before the nation’s highest court.

title: How often do men think about ancient Rome? Quite frequently, it seems.
description: Videos shared on TikTok and Instagram as part of a new trend reveal that many men think about the Roman Empire frequently. But why?

title: Musk expected to meet with Netanyahu as antisemitism controversy rages
description: The planned meeting is the latest effort by Musk friends and allies to head off a growing battle with the Anti-Defamation League.

title: Bizarre AI-generated products are in stores. Here’s how to avoid them.
description: AI-generated self-help books, mugs, wall art and coloring books are filling online marketplaces like Amazon and Etsy as sellers try to make a quick buck.
